\id SNG Matupi Chin Standard Bible
\h SOLOMON LAA
\toc1 SOLOMON LAA
\toc2 Solomon
\toc3 Sol
\mt1 SOLOMON LAA
\mt2 (The Song of Solomon)
\is1 Solomon Laa Kawng
\im Solomon Laa he Laa boeih khuikah Laa Then Koek la a pom sang uh. He laa dongah he hlang ngaih rhoi hlohlailung neh a then hlang a hlainah kawng a thui. Tongpag neh Oila loh amah rhoi tloeptloep hlai uh rhoi. Lungnah te a thangpom tih a hlai. Solomon kah Laa a ti lakah Solomon a hlainah laa coini a ti. Jews rhoek long tah Pathen neh Israel ca a lungnah rhoi la a poek. Khrihca rhoek long tah Khrih neh hlangboel (church) a lungah uh rhoi laa la a khueh. He Laa Bu he 586 \sc b.c\sc* vaengah a tael.
\iot Sawt Yoeinah
\io1 Solomon Laa \ior 1. 1\ior*
\io1 Lungnah rhaipai \ior 1. 2—2. 7\ior*
\io1 Lungnah yin mang \ior 2. 8—3. 5\ior*
\io1 Lungnah hmakhuen \ior 3. 6—6. 10\ior*
\io1 Lungnah lamcawn \ior 6. 11—8. 4\ior*
\io1 Lungnah Thadueng \ior 8. 5-14\ior*
\c 1
\p 
